  • 2.FUNCTIONAL SPECIFICATIONS 

    •  

  • 2.1.Product Features 

    • This website offers the capabilities to the users as belowbelow: 

     

  •  User-friendly design 

  • Browser Compatibility 

  • Farmer Login 

  • Marchant Login 

  •  Product listing 

  • Product Search and filter 

  •  Shopping cart 

  •  payment 

    •  

     

  • 2.2.Functional Requirements 

    • User Class 1 - Non-Registered Users 

      

    2.2.1. [A] Functional Requirement 1 

      

    TITLE: Register as a farmer or Marchant 

    DESC: Non-registered users can create an account by providing personal information, including first name, middle name, last name, gender, profile picture, contact number, birthdate, username, email, and password. After providing these details, users need to verify their email. If the email verification is successful, users are redirected to the login page. 

     

    2.2.1. [B] Functional Requirement 2 

      

    TITLE: Search for Products 

    DESC: Users can utilize the search bar available on the platform to search for desired products. Additionally, users can explore products based on product categories. By entering relevant keywords into the search bar, the platform displays product titles that match the keywords. If no relevant matches are found, a "No products found" message is displayed. 

    Header
    Footer
    5

    2.2.1. [C] Functional Requirement 3 

      

    TITLE: View Product Details 

    DESC: Users can access detailed information about a product, including general product details, seller information, product description, pricing details, as well as delivery and warranty information. 

     

    2.2.1. [D] Functional Requirement 4 

      

    TITLE: Contact Seller(Farmer) 

    DESC: Users can initiate contact with sellers through various social media links associated with the seller's profile. Users are required to provide their name, email, and a message to communicate with the seller. 

     

    User Class 2 - Registered Users 

      

    2.2.2. [A] Functional Requirement 1 

      

    TITLE: Log In to the Platform 

    DESC: Registered users can log in to the system using their credentials. Upon entering a valid username or email along with the correct password, users are successfully logged in. In case of mismatched or invalid credentials, an error message indicating an incorrect username or password is displayed. 

     

    2.2.2. [B] Functional Requirement 2 

      

    TITLE: Explore Product Listings 

    DESC: Users, both registered and non-registered, can utilize the search bar to explore products available in the platform's database. Furthermore, users can browse products by categories, enhancing the accessibility of the platform's offerings. 

     

    2.2.2. [C] Functional Requirement 3 

      

    TITLE: Review Product Details 

    DESC: Users have access to comprehensive product details, including general specifications, seller information, product descriptions, pricing details, delivery information, and warranty particulars, similar to non-registered users. 

     

     

    Header
    Footer
    6

    2.2.2. [D] Functional Requirement 4 

      

    TITLE: Add Product for Sale 

    DESC: Registered users can seamlessly add products for sale by providing essential information. Required details include the product name, category, product image, seller's information, product description, pricing details, product condition, warranty terms, and home delivery information. 

    2.2.2. [E] Functional Requirement 5 

      

    TITLE: View User Profile 

    DESC: Users can access their profile information, including their name, gender, username, email, contact number, birthdate, and profile picture. 

    2.2.2. [F] Functional Requirement 6 

      

    TITLE: Explore Product Dashboard 

    DESC: Users can view a comprehensive dashboard displaying the total count of products listed for sale, products requested for purchase, and offers received for products listed by the user. 

    2.2.2. [G] Functional Requirement 7 

      

    TITLE: Contact Sellers 

    DESC: By clicking on social media links associated with seller profiles, users can initiate contact with sellers. Users need to provide their name, email, and a message to facilitate communication. 

    2.2.2. [H] Functional Requirement 8 

      

    TITLE: Access User Manual 

    DESC: Users can access the website's user manual through the help page. The user manual offers comprehensive instructions on various actions, including registration, password recovery, product search, and seller communication. 

    2.2.2. [H] Functional Requirement 9 

      

    TITLE: Provide Ratings and Reviews 

    DESC: Users have the ability to provide ratings and reviews for both the website and individual products. Utilizing customer reviews as references, users can make informed decisions about their purchases. 

    2.2.2. [I] Functional Requirement 10 

      

    TITLE: Add Products to Cart
